The Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence offered by 4Geeks Academy is a comprehensive program designed for professionals looking to leverage the power of AI in their current roles. This 6-week course covers various aspects of AI, including different types of generative AI, context, prompts, and models. With a focus on real-world applications, participants will learn essential tools and best practices for optimizing AI integration. The course consists of 2 live, online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion, participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop